Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For a guy like him,\Nwhy are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying\Nto get him back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,going so far as to oppose Orochimaru\Nand put your life at risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that? When nobody's ordering\Nyou to do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a special bond\NI was finally able to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, with Orochimaru\Nas your opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nwho the opponent is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If my arms get torn off,\NI'll kick him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If my legs get torn off,\NI'll bite him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If my head gets torn off,\NI'll stare him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If my eyes get torn out,\NI'll curse him in my grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I get chopped up\Ninto pieces...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take Sasuke back\Nfrom Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.43,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(702,610)}Something Important...\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go after\NI create the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:04:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd completely\Ngiven our pursuers the slip...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect no less from\NLord Orochimaru's test subject...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from your condition,\Nit appears you've been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go easy on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't\Nknow that until we try!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- We won't let you interfere!\N- We won't let you interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha...! This is impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess with three against one,\N{\i1}the odds are against me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it appears they've got luck\N{\i1}on their side as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,since it doesn't appear\Nyou've betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it's truly pathetic\Nwatching you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You in particular, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What I mean is, it's futile even\Nif you were able to beat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,People change...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke isn't\Nthe old Sasuke anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the idea...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used to really hate Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it was actually fun\N{\i1}being with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the person who acknowledged me\N{\i1}more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a special bond\N{\i1}I was finally able to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mission\Nwas supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to become the liaison for Danzo\Nand Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,People change...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are things\Nthat don't change...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep a hold on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai... What the heck\Nare you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so hung up\Non your bonds with Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and what are those bonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,From your viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems I can't erase my bond\Nwith my older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The reason why you don't want\N{\i1}to part with that book...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is that you can't forsake yourself\N{\i1}as a younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's because your bonds with\N{\i1}your older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}were that important to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't want to erase the bonds\N{\i1}you have with your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's something\Nthat important to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,then I might understand\Nif I see your bonds with Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys don't know\Nthe real Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably done\Nwith his training right about now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and is in a room deeper\Ninside the hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that Sasuke was\Ntraining with Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think what\Nhe said just now is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!\NThen let's get right to it--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where exactly is\Nthis room deeper inside...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are several rooms\Nscattered about in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A room deeper inside doesn't\Nmean just one or two rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to search\Nevery single one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You might find it\Nif you search at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You could stir up\Na serpent's nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also where Lord Orochimaru's\Nprivate room is, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for speaking honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying the tables\Nwill be turned on us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something we won't know\Nuntil we try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know\Nuntil we try...huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly...pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're going to split up\Nand search for Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura and I on one team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto and Sai on the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If something comes up,\Nbuild up your Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rush in right away\Njust with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang on, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What's with that...look...\N{\i1}you...total...loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You jerk! What're you trying\N{\i1}to look good for, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura's this worried about...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to fight you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For me, you've become...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my closest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like nobody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've...finally made it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
